— This post is definitely out my comfort zone and very vulnerable for me but I am so grateful for the body changes that brought me my sweet cohen and I hope I can encourage other women to feel beautiful when they look at themselves— I know, easier said than done, but remind yourself of the life you created and how beautiful they are. I will forever be reminded that my body grew and carried my beautiful son for a long 9 months and I am SO proud of that! I hate the stigma around stretch marks and body changes durning/after pregnancy… hello!!! you grew a LIFE and you should be so proud of that. Stretch marks are normal, your body changing is normal, you are not alone and you are so beautiful. 🫶🏻🤰🏻✨👶🏻
